<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('../partials/header') %>
<body class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-100">

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="px-6 py-24 text-center bg-gray-900">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Precision. Flexibility. Chemistry.</h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">We deliver tailored chemical solutions for research, industry, and beyond.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Company Overview -->
  <section class="bg-gray-800 px-6 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6 text-white">Who We Are</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Chemten, Ltd. is a chemical company based in Slovakia, specializing in the preparation of organic compounds designed to meet specific customer requirements.
        Our focus is on providing high-quality, adaptable, and cost-effective solutions across a wide range of scientific and industrial sectors.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission and Capabilities -->
  <section class="bg-gray-900 px-6 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Our Mission</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          We aim to make specialized chemistry more accessible. By balancing precision with flexibility, we provide reliable products that meet demanding needs — without compromising performance or affordability.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">What We Do</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Our expertise covers a broad spectrum of organic synthesis. From custom formulations and rare intermediates to challenging or hazardous compounds — we welcome requests and conduct feasibility research for compounds not listed in our catalogue.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Specialization Highlight -->
  <section class="bg-gray-800 px-6 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6 text-white">Built for Custom Chemistry</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We’re not just a supplier — we’re a synthesis partner. Our infrastructure is designed to handle demanding projects, including toxic, sensitive, or highly specialized compounds. If it’s possible to make, we’ll find a way.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Subtle History Mention -->
  <section class="bg-gray-900 px-6 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">A New Chapter, Backed by Experience</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Though Chemten is a newly formed entity, our foundation is built upon two decades of chemical industry experience. We combine fresh energy with proven expertise to meet today’s challenges with confidence.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>
